    "content_hash": "5d5b346d2610e2f1",
    "department": "GTM",
    "description": "ABOUT FLORA\n\nWe build creative tools for the new creative class—an intelligent canvas where the best AI models enable professional craft. We're a team of ~20, with $52M of capital raised from exceptional investors like Redpoint Ventures, Hanabi Capital, Menlo Ventures, Justin Kan, and Gabe Whaley (founder of MSCHF). Our customers span a variety of creative industries and include Pentagram, Lionsgate, and Nike.\n\n\nABOUT THE ROLE\n\nWe're looking for a Social Media Lead to own FLORA's voice, growth, and presence on Instagram, X, and LinkedIn. You'll be responsible for growing our followership and turning social into a true growth engine for the business. You'll orchestrate our social presence (including product launches, creator collaborations, industry commentary, and growth experiments) into a consistent rhythm that builds our brand. You'll moderate our channels, track what competitors are doing, and ensure FLORA stays ahead.\n\nThis is a high-ownership, autonomous role. You'll write compelling copy, create content, and post independently. You own how FLORA shows up on social media and are trusted to make brand decisions in real-time.\n\n\nWHAT YOU’LL OWN\n\nSocial Strategy \u0026 Channel Growth\n\n - Own strategy, content, and growth across Instagram, X (Twitter), and LinkedIn\n\n - Drive follower growth and turn social into a top-of-funnel acquisition channel that converts audiences into FLORA signups\n\n - Run experiments, analyze metrics, and optimize for engagement and reach\n\n - Build repeatable content systems that drive consistent output and results\n\nBrand Voice \u0026 Copywriting\n\n - Be the voice of FLORA - write sharp, engaging copy that sounds distinctly like us\n\n - Shape our narrative and create content that resonates with our community\n\n - Post independently with strong brand judgment\n\nViral Content \u0026 Cultural Relevance\n\n - Craft posts, threads, and videos that get shared and drive meaningful engagement\n\n - Stay plugged into AI, creative tools, and internet culture\n\n - Spot timely moments and turn them into high-performing content\n\nContent Creation \u0026 Execution\n\n - Create content yourself or guide Creative Producers to execute your vision\n\n - Write threads, edit videos, design graphics—whatever's needed to ship quality content fast\n\n - Iterate quickly based on what works\n\nMarket Intelligence\n\n - Track AI news, creative tech trends, and competitive landscape\n\n - Synthesize insights into content opportunities and strategic recommendations\n\n\nWHAT WE'RE LOOKING FOR\n\nProven Social Media Operator\n\n - Proven experience building or scaling social channels, ideally somewhere with a strong creative community\n\n - Demonstrated ability to grow accounts and create high-performing content\n\nExceptional Writer \u0026 Brand Voice\n\n - Strong copywriter who can craft compelling, on-brand content that drives engagement\n\n - Able to shape brand perception through consistent, authentic voice\n\nDeep Platform Expertise\n\n - Understand what works on X vs. Instagram vs. LinkedIn (algorithms, formats, trends)\n\n - Tailor content for each platform while maintaining brand consistency\n\nEye for Viral Content\n\n - You’ve made content go viral and understand what makes people share\n\nMetrics-Driven\n\n - Track performance, analyze data, and optimize for growth\n\n - Treat social as a business growth lever, not just brand awareness\n\nScrappy with a Testing Mindset\n\n - Ship quickly, iterate based on feedback, comfortable with ambiguity\n\n - Operate independently without waiting for permission\n\nStrong Creative Judgment\n\n - Trusted to post without oversight while maintaining brand consistency\n\n - Balance experimentation with brand standards\n\nVersatile Creator\n\n - You can create content yourself (video editing, design, FLORA)\n\nMarket Aware\n\n - Follow AI and creative tech trends, know what our audience cares about\n\nOwnership Mindset\n\n - Act like an owner: high standards, proactive, accountable for results\n\nPassionate About AI Creativity\n\n - Excited about FLORA's mission and spreading our vision\n\n\nWHY THIS ROLE MATTERS\n\nSocial is where we tell the FLORA story and share our work with the world. It's where we bring the creative community together, spark conversation about the future of creative work, and show what's possible when AI is built for real creatives. Done right, our channels become where creatives come to learn, get inspired, and see what's next in the generative era.\n",
    "employment_type": "FullTime",
    "is_active": true,
